# services/weather_api/.dockerignore — applied to the build context
# (the repo root, since the Dockerfile is invoked from there).

.git
.dart_tool
**/.dart_tool
**/build
**/coverage
**/*.log
**/test
**/Dockerfile
**/.dockerignore
**/README.md
**/CHANGELOG.md

# Local IDE / OS noise
.idea
.vscode
.DS_Store

# Keep this directory's Dockerfile out of the build context — it is
# read by Docker via -f and doesn't need to land inside the image.
